metadata.name: Flakestate - I Was Wrong To Assume #1/22
metadata.description:
Recorded in 2019 and released on January 1st, 2020 as a single.  
2 Years later in 2022, this is the first Flakestate production to be released as an NFT.

This attitude - love - has got a remarkably long way to go

to assume
